name: Dark crytal tower
description: [ENG] - the dark crystal tower is a work that brings part of my regionality, I am from Recife - PE and one of the marks of my city is the sculpture park where the artist Francisco Brennand idealized and placed the crystal tower as "the jewel of the crown", where it was opened in 2000. I made this linocut because it permeates the imaginary of the environment where I live, and it is a very beautiful work. - [PT/BR] - a torre de cristal escuro Ã© uma obra que tras uma parte da minha regiona
